Package: Earthquakes
Type: Package
Title: Analyzes and Visualizes Earthquake Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christopher Pearson
Maintainer: The package maintainer <cmpear@uw.edu>
Description: Takes in quake data from National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration. 
    Includes two ggplot2 visuals for the data: one for generating timelines, and the other for generating maps of quake data.
    NOAA website: https://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/nndc/struts/form?t=101650&s=1&d=1.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
